DNS Recon:
----------

#dnsrecon -h

#dnsrecon -d google.com
we get all the records

----------------------------------------

DNS Enum:
---------

#dnsenum -h

#dnsenum google.com
it will give:
host address
name server
mail server
trying zone transfers
bruteforce with the wordlist file /usr/share/dnsenum/dns.txt to find subdomain enumeration
find class C netranges
perform reverse lookup for the founded class C IPs


#dnsenum -f <filename>
to find subdomains with ip with the manual wordlist file

